text: Ani tya strine, jicya ghari yusupha hote, yusuphala phusalavane suru kele, jenekaruna tyane apalya manavara taba thevane soduna dyave ani dara banda karuna ti mhanu lagali, ya (javala) ya. (Yusupha) mhanale, allaha raksana karo! To majha palanakarta ahe. Tyane mala khupa cangalya prakare thevale ahe. Niscitaca an'yaya karanaryance kadapi bhale hota nahi
